{
  "number": 3095,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/3095",
  "title": "Clean HTML output",
  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for participating in this project! We will try to answer as soon as possible 🙏\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe 🙏**\r\n\r\nThe current HTML output of InstantSearch.js contains whitespaces, which makes it messy.\r\n\r\n![before](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6137112/45218734-f0dc0100-b2a8-11e8-963a-00d1f64d708a.png)\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like 🤔**\r\n\r\nBy trimming the templates [once compiled by Hogan](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/develop/src/lib/utils.js#L182), we could clean the HTML output by removing the whitespaces.\r\n\r\n```diff\r\n return hogan\r\n     .compile(template, compileOptions)\r\n     .render({\r\n       ...data,\r\n       helpers: transformedHelpers,\r\n     })\r\n+    .trim();\r\n```\r\n\r\n![after](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6137112/45218819-2d0f6180-b2a9-11e8-9bbc-49a28cb6e0df.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered ✨**\r\n\r\nWe could also use [Handlebars' whitespace control](http://handlebarsjs.com/expressions.html#whitespace-control) features but I didn't get this to work.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n\r\nIf we go for this in InstantSearch 3, we'd need to apply this change after having merged the InstantSearch.css specs because it'd also clean up some snapshots.\r\n\r\n```diff\r\n <div\r\n   dangerouslySetInnerHTML={\r\n     Object {\r\n-      \"__html\": \"  $\",\r\n+      \"__html\": \"$\",\r\n     }\r\n   }\r\n />\r\n <div\r\n   dangerouslySetInnerHTML={\r\n     Object {\r\n-      \"__html\": \"  \",\r\n+      \"__html\": \"\",\r\n      }\r\n   }\r\n />\r\n```\r\n",
